fields.text: The best way to get started is to quit talking and start doing.
fields.author: Walt Disney

fields.text: Don't let yesterday take too much of today.
fields.author: Will Rogers

fields.text: Success is not in what you have but in what you are.
fields.author: Bo Benneth

fields.text: You miss 100%of the shots you don't take.
fields.author: Wayne Gretze

fields.text: Don't watch the clock; do what it dose. Keep going.
fields.author: sam Leveson

fields.text: Success is not final, failure is not fatal: It is the courage to continue that counts.
fields.author: Walt Disney
